      <div class="govspeak">
<p>This information helps Home Office ministers and policy-makers address the concerns of ordinary citizens. It also helps the police, the courts and immigration officials to do their jobs as effectively as possible.</p>

<h2 id="research-series">Research series</h2>

<p>Home Office manages the following research series:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/home-office/series/alcohol-and-drug-research-and-analysis">alcohol and drug research and analysis</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/fire-and-rescue-research-and-analysis">fire and rescue research and analysis</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/home-office/series/crime-research-and-analysis">crime research and analysis</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/home-office/series/counter-terrorism-research-and-analysis">counter terrorism research and analysis</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/home-office/series/migration-research-and-analysis">migration research and analysis</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/home-office/series/policing-research-and-analysis">policing research and analysis</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="about-home-office-science">About Home Office Science</h2>
<p>Home Office science group is part of the Home Office that brings together the departmentâ€™s scientists, researchers and analysts. Read our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/home-office/series/home-office-science-standards" title="Home Office Science standards.">standards and style guide</a></p>

<h2 id="archived-research-and-analysis">Archived research and analysis</h2>

<p>GOV.UK has the most recent Home Office research and analysis. Home Office research and analysis from before May 2010 are found on the <a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20110218135832/http://rds.homeoffice.gov.uk/rds/index.html">National Archives research development and statistics</a> website.</p>
